  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Digital Marketing / Executive",
  "description": "<p>Established integrated communications company is seeking a suitable candidate who is\ninterested in crafting a career in the digital marketing field.</p><p>Job Description</p><p>The selected candidate is a self-starter and passionate about marketing with strong\nknowledge on all aspects of digital marketing including:</p><ul><li>Website marketing campaign</li><li>Search marketing</li><li>Paid search advertising</li><li>Social media marketing</li><li>Content marketing</li><li>Mobile marketing</li></ul><p>The incumbent is expected to develop and implement the company’s digital marketing\nand communications business strategy to complement our integrated communications business.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>· Responsible for planning and implementing digital marketing plans and strategies to achieve\ncorporate goals.</p><p>· Able to conceptualise and pitch ideas for clients to visualise and understand how our digital services can help them reach their target audience with key messages.</p><p>· Able to support clients in developing online and mobile digital marketing strategies.</p><p>· Conduct market research and competitive analyses of target markets to identify new\nbusiness opportunities and drive results.</p><p>· Establish contact and developing relationships with prospects and recommend solutions for clients.</p><p>· Establish and build networks with partners and collaborate to develop new business.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>· Diploma/degree in Marketing, Business, e-commerce or Infocomm Technology.</p><p>· At least two years working experience in social media or digital marketing.</p><p>· Familiar with digital marketing tools such as social media technologies, online marketing,\nanalytics, SEO, mobile apps etc. </p><p>· Good communication and presentation skills</p><p>Advantage</p><p>Priority consideration will be given to candidates with: </p><p>· Minimum two years management experience </p><p>· Experience in setting up new business either as a start-up or new division within a company</p><p>Interested applicants submit applications and resume to: <a href=\"mailto:hr@equity.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@equity.com.sg</a></p>",
